Chat App p2p
============

Usage 
-----

    $ go run main.go [ options ]
    $ go build
    $ ./name-executable [ options ]

CLI Options
-----------

    --nick    : nickname of user ($Env:USERNAME or $Env:USER)
    --channel : channel name to join at the connection ( d√©faut: #ibug )
    --debug   : display more debug informations

List of Chat commands
---------------------

    /help     : display user help
    /clear    : clean the current terminal window buffer
    /exit     : quit the chat
